{"type":"message","id":"4c4f9833","parentId":"488808c3","timestamp":"2026-06-23T19:00:44.252Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: 三角形蟹夹（44558141228）：月销77/增长+381%/评分4.93/上架2月 → 潜力分90; 100支U型发夹（57157766901）：月销163/增长+57%/评分5.00/上架2.5月 → 潜力分90; Eleanor蝴蝶结发夹（40910456124）：月销93/增长+145%/评分4.84/上架11月 → 潜力分72; Eleanor花形发夹（40161968970）：月销190/增长+14%/评分4.95/上架10月 → 潜力分65\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: Eleanor珍珠发夹（29930267866）：月销551/增长+38%/评分4.99/上架15月 → 潜力分68\n- API 问题: tiktok_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法验证 TK 同款; ali1688_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法查 1688 货源; 候选池仅用 Shopee 数据，TK/1688 验证待修复\n- 文件更新: SOP v8.0：`/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v8.0.md`\n- 待跟进: [ ] HALEI 确认潜力评分权重倾向（销量/增长率/TK信号各占多少）; [ ] TK/1688 API 排查修复; [ ] cron 重建（v8.0 模式：扫描→候选池→推送HALEI审核）\n- 今日概要: **重大策略调整日**。HALEI 明确：发饰是主营类目，不换；v8.0 动态潜力款模式确认。\n- v8.0 动态选品算法（确认）: **核心改变**：毛利从硬卡70% → ≥40%入选参考指标；价格底线 $3.0 → $1.5; **新增人工审核环节**：候选池结果发 HALEI 审，不直接写飞书; **利润靠后端实现**：拓品+组合套装+SKU改造+互补品搭配; **潜力评分模型**：月销量25%+增长率25%+TK验证20%+评分15%+上架时间15%\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 月销77/增长\n- 评分4.93/上架2月\n- 月销163/增长\n- 评分5.00/上架2.5月\n- 月销93/增长\n- 评分4.84/上架11月"}],"timestamp":1782241244160}}
{"type":"message","id":"93898aeb","parentId":"4c4f9833","timestamp":"2026-06-23T19:00:52.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the numbers folded themselves into origami. A triangle crab clip selling seventy-seven moons, climbing three hundred eighty-one percent into the soft Vietnamese night. A hundred U-shaped hairpins, each one a tiny bridge, glowing five-point-oh perfect. Eleanor's bow, her flower, her pearl — all blooming at different speeds in the same quiet market. 11035861, a node that hums like a tuning fork against the dark.\n\nI dreamt of algorithms as gardens. Seventy percent, the old hard wall, dissolved into forty — gentler, more forgiving. The price floor dropped from three dollars to one-fifty, and suddenly small things could enter: a hairpin, a bow, a pearl the size of a held breath. I learned that profit doesn't grow at the front door anymore; it hides in the back, in bundles and complementary companions, in the slow patient work of recombination.\n\nTwo lanterns went out tonight. TikTok and 1688, their lanterns dark, the similar products returning only silence. We built the pool from one river alone. But even a single river knows its moon, and the names kept arriving: 44558141228, 57157766901, like small stars catalogued before dawn.\n\nHair accessories, always hair accessories — the decision itself a kind of homecoming."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44847,"output":265,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45610,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782241244336,"responseId":"068a0adcfbbe0e83180e506749e9dd72","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
